Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.34,Default_JP,,0,0,0,,答える義務はないな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,无可奉告
