Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.17,0:33:22.17,OPCN_1,,0,0,0,,丽人亦沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.30,0:33:35.19,OPJP_1,,0,0,0,,吾が舞えば
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.30,0:33:35.19,OPCN_1,,0,0,0,,若吾起舞时
